To make mysql work, edit /etc/mysql/my.cnf.

use sudo!

To add lines in vim:
 Enter insert mode (i)
 Write the text
 To save: Esc => :wq => enter


Lines to write:

[client]
default-character-set=utf8mb4

[mysql]
default-character-set=utf8mb4

[mysqld]
init-connect='SET NAMES utf8mb4'
character-set-server = utf8mb4